Changelog
=========
0.1.3 (2015-03-03)
--------------------

- Added support for Summary Large Image and Photo Cards.

0.1.2 (2015-02-03)
--------------------

- Documentation added.

0.1.1 (2015-02-02)
--------------------

- Added twitter viewlet and various settings to be able to select what type of
  card should be used for a certain content type.

0.1 (2015-01-30)
--------------------

- Initial release.


